author: COMSOL
description: An Epoxy Mold Compound covering a MEMS pressure sensor is subject to moisture absorption. A time-dependent study calculates the moisture diffusion in the mold compound and a parametric stationary analysis calculates the drift on measured pressure induced by hygroscopic swelling.
